00:30:01.299 --> 00:30:05.530
last forever. If we can't prove that this
stuff is working for our clients, there's

00:30:05.530 --> 00:30:09.580
only so much money they're gonna put behind
it. So, we need to make sure that we build

00:30:09.580 --> 00:30:13.470
the right measurement plans into all of these
deals that we're creating.

00:30:13.470 --> 00:30:18.190
And the other thing is messaging and making
sure that we have the right messaging for

00:30:18.190 --> 00:30:22.710
the different platforms. So, we can't just
take our TV creative and run it online and

00:30:22.710 --> 00:30:27.240
take pieces of it and shorten it. So, making
sure, which is why the creatives need to be

00:30:27.240 --> 00:30:31.230
involved from the very beginning, is if we're
recommending all these platforms for our clients

00:30:31.230 --> 00:30:35.080
and they creatively need to be making sure
